    inLove: "Capricorn in love is slower to open than most signs — they approach relationships with the same careful evaluation they bring to everything. Once committed, they are extraordinarily loyal and will show their love through practical care and long-term investment. The challenge: their tendency to prioritize work and achievement can leave partners feeling secondary. They need someone who respects their ambition without competing with it. Best matched with Taurus and Virgo (earth signs who value commitment), and Scorpio and Pisces who offer emotional depth.",
